<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>JESUH NIH A RALKAP A HRUAI HNA CH34</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ngai u! aunak thawng cu, &quot;Hodah a kal lai?&quot; Mi ka khawmhsuat lio ah,
 Aih, nan ti hnga maw? Ka puanlang cu lek in hmaisuang dohnak ah; Pathian
 le dinnak tanh in hodah kal lai?

[C1]
   Jesuh nih a hruai hna, a ralkap bu cu, Ral an tei in dinnak vawlei a
   khat lai.

[V2]
 Pathian thawnnak bochan in ral kan tei lai. Satan ralkap an tho, Ral
 thuam i hruk u, A thiang le a dingmi cu kan dirpi lai; Pathian lei ah
 tang in ral cu do u si.

[C2]
   Jesuh nih a hruai hna, a ralkap bu cu, Ral an tei in dinnak vawlei a
   khat lai.

[V3]
 Rel cawk lo van ralkap hlasak in an ra. &quot;Kan hruaitu Siangpahrang
 thangthat si ko seh&quot; Hmuitinh thiang he ka kip in kan i kom cang; An
 hlasak thawng ngai u, dohnak ah kal u.

[C3]
   Jesuh nih a hruai hna, a ralkap bu cu, Ral an tei in dinnak vawlei a
   khat lai.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<hymn_number>34</hymn_number>
</song>